    "google_quiche": {
        "_comment": "Patterns for Google QUICHE (Chrome/Cronet). Mangled C++ symbols, pattern scanning for stripped binaries (e.g. libmonochrome_64.so). Labels match LABEL_TO_KEY in agent/quic/shared/google_quiche_offsets.ts. Filled per-build by BoringSecretHunter. Per-target patterns can be overridden by passing --patterns <user.json>; user entries replace the matching key (loader.deep_merge replaces leaf lists, does not append).",
